#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn55.9"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn55.9:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 55 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 55 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn55.9:0.2"
msgid "1. Veḷudvāravagga "
msgstr "1. At Bamboo Gate "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn55.9:0.3"
msgid "9. Dutiyagiñjakāvasathasutta "
msgstr "9. At the Brick Hall (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.358, sc1
msgctxt "sn55.9:1.1"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā ānando bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Ānanda said to the Buddha: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn55.9:1.2"
msgid "“asoko nāma, bhante, bhikkhu kālaṅkato; "
msgstr "“Sir, the monk named Asoka has passed away. "

msgctxt "sn55.9:1.3"
msgid "tassa kā gati, ko abhisamparāyo? "
msgstr "Where has he been reborn in his next life? "

msgctxt "sn55.9:1.4"
msgid "Asokā nāma, bhante, bhikkhunī kālaṅkatā … pe … "
msgstr "The nun named Asokā, "

msgctxt "sn55.9:1.5"
msgid "asoko nāma, bhante, upāsako kālaṅkato … pe … "
msgstr "the layman named Asoka, "

msgctxt "sn55.9:1.6"
msgid "asokā nāma, bhante, upāsikā kālaṅkatā; "
msgstr "and the laywoman named Asokā have passed away. "

msgctxt "sn55.9:1.7"
msgid "tassā kā gati, ko abhisamparāyo”ti? "
msgstr "Where have they been reborn in the next life?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn55.9:2.1"
msgid "“Asoko, ānanda, bhikkhu kālaṅkato āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja vihāsi … pe … "
msgstr "“Ānanda, the monk Asoka passed away having realized the undefiled freedom of heart and freedom by wisdom in this very life … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn55.9:2.2"
msgid "(purimaveyyākaraṇena ekanidānaṃ.) "
msgstr "(And all is explained as in SN 55.8) "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn55.9:3.1"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho so, ānanda, dhammādāso dhammapariyāyo; "
msgstr "This is that mirror of the teaching. "

msgctxt "sn55.9:3.2"
msgid "yena samannāgato ariyasāvako ākaṅkhamāno attanāva attānaṃ byākareyya: "
msgstr "A noble disciple who has this may declare of themselves: "

msgctxt "sn55.9:3.3"
msgid "‘khīṇanirayomhi khīṇatiracchānayoni khīṇapettivisayo khīṇāpāyaduggativinipāto, sotāpannohamasmi avinipātadhammo niyato sambodhiparāyaṇo’”ti. "
msgstr "‘I’ve finished with rebirth in hell, the animal realm, and the ghost realm. I’ve finished with all places of loss, bad places, the underworld. I am a stream-enterer! I’m not liable to be reborn in the underworld, and am bound for awakening.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn55.9:3.4"
msgid "Navamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
